data.allRelevantTextIncludingURLs: Better Lovers will be performing at Wonder Ballroom, Portland, Oregon on Wed Nov 27. Show starts at 7pm, doors at 6pm. Tickets can be purchased [here](https://www.etix.com/ticket/p/64150342/better-lovers-the-highly-irresponsible-tour-portland-wonder-ballroom?partner_id=100) and more information is available [here](https://monqui.com/event/better-lovers-the-highly-irresponsible-tour/wonder-ballroom/portland-oregon/).
